pageContext.claim: “In the last month alone, we added another 250,000 jobs, and nearly a half a million Americans -- it's now going to be almost 600,000 Americans returned to the workforce.”
pageContext.analysis: Just in August, 286,000 jobs were created. The jobs number topped 250,000 two earlier months in 2018. And Obama had four months above 250,000 in 2016, when Trump was telling audiences that the economy was lousy.
